   275â†’## 3. Animation & Motion Systems
   276â†’
   277â†’### Centralized Animation Tokens
   278â†’
   279â†’**Sources:**
   280â†’- https://motion.dev/docs/react-tailwind
   281â†’- https://tailwindcss.com/docs/animation
   282â†’
   283â†’#### Architecture Strategy: Tailwind for Static, Motion for Dynamic
   284â†’
   285â†’**Key Principle:** Let each library do what it does best:
   286â†’- **Tailwind:** Static animations (transitions, keyframes)
   287â†’- **Motion/Vue Animations:** Dynamic, interactive animations (gestures, layout shifts)
   288â†’
   289â†’#### Tailwind Animation Configuration
   290â†’
   291â†’**Define Animation Tokens:**
   292â†’```css
   293â†’@theme {
   294â†’  /* Animation durations */
   295â†’  --animate-duration-fast: 150ms;
   296â†’  --animate-duration-base: 300ms;
   297â†’  --animate-duration-slow: 500ms;
   298â†’
   299â†’  /* Easing functions */
   300â†’  --ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
   301â†’  --ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
   302â†’
   303â†’  /* Predefined animations */
   304â†’  --animate-fade-in: fade-in var(--animate-duration-base) var(--ease-in-out);
   305â†’  --animate-slide-up: slide-up var(--animate-duration-base) var(--ease-in-out);
   306â†’  --animate-scale-in: scale-in var(--animate-duration-fast) var(--ease-spring);
   307â†’
   308â†’  @keyframes fade-in {
   309â†’    from { opacity: 0; }
   310â†’    to { opacity: 1; }
   311â†’  }
   312â†’
   313â†’  @keyframes slide-up {
   314â†’    from {
   315â†’      opacity: 0;
   316â†’      transform: translateY(1rem);
   317â†’    }
   318â†’    to {
   319â†’      opacity: 1;
   320â†’      transform: translateY(0);
   321â†’    }
   322â†’  }
   323â†’
   324â†’  @keyframes scale-in {
   325â†’    from {
   326â†’      opacity: 0;
   327â†’      transform: scale(0.95);
   328â†’    }
   329â†’    to {
   330â†’      opacity: 1;
   331â†’      transform: scale(1);
   332â†’    }
   333â†’  }
   334â†’}
   335â†’```
   336â†’
   337â†’**Usage:**
   338â†’```html
   339â†’<div class="animate-fade-in">Fades in on load</div>
   340â†’<div class="animate-slide-up hover:animate-scale-in">Interactive</div>
   341â†’```
