   491â†’## 4. Astro + Vue + Tailwind Integration
   492â†’
   493â†’### SSR-Safe Tailwind Patterns
   494â†’
   495â†’**Sources:**
   496â†’- https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/styling/
   497â†’- https://themefisher.com/tailwind-css-with-astro
   498â†’
   499â†’#### Setup Configuration
   500â†’
   501â†’**Install Tailwind:**
