   563â†’
   564â†’#### Dark Mode Implementation (SSR-Safe)
   565â†’
   566â†’**Source:** https://namoku.dev/blog/darkmode-tailwind-astro/
   567â†’
   568â†’**Critical Pattern: Inline Script for Flash Prevention**
   569â†’
   570â†’```astro
   571â†’---
   572â†’// src/layouts/Layout.astro
   573â†’import '../styles/global.css';
   574â†’---
   575â†’
   576â†’<!doctype html>
   577â†’<html lang="en">
   578â†’  <head>
   579â†’    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
   580â†’    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
   581â†’    <title>{title}</title>
   582â†’
   583â†’    <!-- CRITICAL: Inline script runs before page render -->
   584â†’    <script is:inline>
   585â†’      // IIFE to prevent global scope pollution
   586â†’      (function() {
   587â†’        const getTheme = () => {
   588â†’          // Check localStorage first
   589â†’          if (typeof localStorage !== 'undefined') {
   590â†’            const stored = localStorage.getItem('theme');
   591â†’            if (stored) return stored;
   592â†’          }
   593â†’
   594â†’          // Fall back to system preference
   595â†’          return window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches
   596â†’            ? 'dark'
   597â†’            : 'light';
   598â†’        };
   599â†’
   600â†’        const theme = getTheme();
   601â†’
   602â†’        // Apply dark class immediately (before render)
   603â†’        if (theme === 'dark') {
   604â†’          document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
   605â†’        }
   606â†’      })();
   607â†’    </script>
   608â†’  </head>
   609â†’  <body>
   610â†’    <slot />
   611â†’  </body>
   612â†’</html>
   613â†’```
   614â†’
   615â†’**âš ï¸ Key Point:** The `is:inline` directive prevents Astro from bundling/optimizing the script, ensuring it runs synchronously before page render.
   616â†’
   617â†’#### View Transitions Dark Mode Persistence
   618â†’
   619â†’**Problem:** Astro View Transitions API replaces DOM content, removing the `dark` class.
   620â†’
   621â†’**Solution:**
   622â†’```astro
   623â†’<script>
   624â†’  // Theme toggle logic
   625â†’  function applyTheme() {
   626â†’    const theme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
   627â†’    document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark', theme === 'dark');
   628â†’  }
   629â†’
   630â†’  function toggleTheme() {
   631â†’    const currentTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
   632â†’    const newTheme = currentTheme === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
   633â†’    localStorage.setItem('theme', newTheme);
   634â†’    applyTheme();
   635â†’  }
   636â†’
   637â†’  // Apply on initial load
   638â†’  applyTheme();
   639â†’
   640â†’  // Reapply after View Transitions navigation
   641â†’  document.addEventListener('astro:after-swap', () => {
   642â†’    applyTheme();
   643â†’
   644â†’    // Reattach event listeners (removed during swap)
   645â†’    const themeToggle = document.getElementById('themeToggle');
   646â†’    if (themeToggle && !themeToggle.hasAttribute('onclick')) {
   647â†’      themeToggle.addEventListener('click', toggleTheme);
   648â†’    }
   649â†’  });
   650â†’</script>
   651â†’
   652â†’<button id="themeToggle" type="button">
   653â†’  Toggle Theme
   654â†’</button>
   655â†’```
   656â†’
   657â†’**Event Lifecycle:**
   658â†’- `astro:before-preparation` - Before new page fetch
   659â†’- `astro:after-preparation` - After new page fetch
   660â†’- `astro:before-swap` - Before DOM replacement
   661â†’- **`astro:after-swap`** - **Use this for theme persistence**
   662â†’- `astro:page-load` - After navigation complete
   663â†’
   664â†’#### Vue Component Tailwind Class Hydration
   665â†’
   666â†’**SSR-Safe Pattern:**
   667â†’```vue
   668â†’<script setup lang="ts">
   669â†’import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue';
   670â†’
   671â†’// Safe: Static classes (hydrated correctly)
   672â†’const baseClasses = 'bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded';
   673â†’
   674â†’// Dangerous: Dynamic classes computed during SSR
   675â†’// const dynamicClasses = computed(() => {
   676â†’//   return isDark.value ? 'bg-gray-900' : 'bg-white'; // âŒ SSR mismatch
   677â†’// });
   678â†’
   679â†’// Safe: Dynamic classes after mount
   680â†’const themeClasses = ref('');
   681â†’
   682â†’onMounted(() => {
   683â†’  const theme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
   684â†’  themeClasses.value = theme === 'dark' ? 'bg-gray-900' : 'bg-white';
   685â†’});
   686â†’</script>
   687â†’
   688â†’<template>
   689â†’  <button :class="[baseClasses, themeClasses]">
   690â†’    Click me
