  1115â†’## 7. Key Takeaways & Action Items
  1116â†’
  1117â†’### Immediate Implementation Steps
  1118â†’
  1119â†’1. **Migrate to Tailwind v4 CSS Configuration**
  1120â†’   - Replace `tailwind.config.js` theme with `@theme` directive
  1121â†’   - Define semantic color tokens with dark mode variants
  1122â†’   - Use `@utility` for custom utilities instead of plugins
  1123â†’
  1124â†’2. **Implement SSR-Safe Dark Mode**
