  1128â†’
  1129â†’3. **Centralize Animation System**
  1130â†’   - Define animation tokens via `@theme` (durations, easings, keyframes)
  1131â†’   - Create Vue composables for Transition class sets
  1132â†’   - Implement `prefers-reduced-motion` checks
  1133â†’
  1134â†’4. **Organize Global Styles**
  1135â†’   - Single import in layout component (`src/styles/global.css`)
