  1139â†’
  1140â†’5. **Adopt Semantic Color Naming**
  1141â†’   - Replace literal names (`blue-500`) with role-based (`primary`, `foreground`)
  1142â†’   - Define dark mode as CSS variable overrides
  1143â†’   - Use HSL format for opacity modifier support
  1144â†’
  1145â†’### Anti-Patterns to Avoid
  1146â†’
  1147â†’âŒ **Don't:** Compute Tailwind classes dynamically during SSR
  1148â†’```vue
