  1172â†’---
  1173â†’```
  1174â†’
  1175â†’---
  1176â†’
  1177â†’âŒ **Don't:** Create plugins for simple utilities
  1178â†’```javascript
  1179â†’// Over-engineered
  1180â†’plugin(({ addUtilities }) => {
  1181â†’  addUtilities({ '.content-auto': { 'content-visibility': 'auto' } });
  1182â†’});
  1183â†’```
  1184â†’
  1185â†’âœ… **Do:** Use `@utility` directive
  1186â†’```css
