  1196â†’module.exports = {
  1197â†’  theme: {
  1198â†’    colors: { primary: '#3f3cbb' } // âŒ Removes all default colors
  1199â†’  }
  1200â†’}
  1201â†’```
  1202â†’
  1203â†’âœ… **Do:** Use `@theme` to extend
  1204â†’```css
  1205â†’@theme {
  1206â†’  --color-primary: #3f3cbb; /* âœ… Adds to defaults */
  1207â†’}
  1208â†’```
  1209â†’
  1210â†’### Performance Optimizations
  1211â†’
  1212â†’1. **Purge Unused Styles**
  1213â†’   - Ensure `content` array includes all template files
  1214â†’   - Use PurgeCSS safelist for dynamic classes
